---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Harmonium Halt"
  description="Harmonium Halt privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  noindex={false}
>
  <div class="bg-white border-b border-ebony/8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-3 text-xs text-ebony/40">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-saffron-600">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">›</span>
      <span class="text-ebony/70">Privacy Policy</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-display font-black text-3xl text-ebony mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-ebony/50 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: December 10, 2024</p>
    <div class="prose-harmonium space-y-6 text-ebony/70 leading-relaxed">
      <p>Harmonium Halt ("we", "us", or "our") operates the website <a href="https://www.harmoniumhalt.com" class="text-saffron-600">www.harmoniumhalt.com</a>. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our website.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>Automatically Collected Information:</strong> When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain information about your device, including your browser type, IP address, referring URLs, and pages visited. This data is used for analytics and to improve our website.</p>
      <p><strong>Contact Form Information:</strong> When you submit our contact form, we collect your name, email address, and message content solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>
      <p><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies to analyze site traffic and improve your experience. You may disable cookies through your browser settings, though some features may not function properly.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>To provide and improve the Harmonium Halt website and services</li>
        <li>To respond to your inquiries and support requests</li>
        <li>To analyze usage patterns and optimize content</li>
        <li>To ensure website security and prevent abuse</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share anonymized, aggregate data with analytics providers to understand site usage. We may disclose information when required by law.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>Our website may use third-party services including Google Analytics and YouTube embeds. These services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them. YouTube videos embedded on our site are subject to Google's privacy policy.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Web Audio API</h2>
      <p>Our web harmonium uses the Web Audio API built into your browser. No audio data is transmitted to our servers — all sound processing happens locally on your device.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Harmonium Halt is designed for general audiences and suitable for learners of all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete personal information we hold about you. To exercise these rights, contact us at hello@harmoniumhalt.com.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of significant changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ebony mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:hello@harmoniumhalt.com" class="text-saffron-600">hello@harmoniumhalt.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
